extendedInfo.description: Turtles are reptiles of the order Testudines. characterised by a special bony or cartilaginous shell developed from their ribs that acts as a shield. "Turtle" may either refer to the Testudines as a whole, or to particular Testudines which make up a form taxon that is not monophyletic. Here we have taken amazing wallpaper of turtle and transform it into a 3D cube Live Wallpaper. Feattures include:Options for transparent box2 different light sourceOption to move lightOption to change viewing angle and change background color.Option for Auto rotation with speed control, or manual control with finger swipe.Contain Ads
